<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Midnights with Maddie</title>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
      background: #080008;
      color: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255, 220, 150, 0.25), transparent 35%),
        linear-gradient(to bottom, #1a0018, #050005);
    }

    .curtain {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      width: 26%;
      height: 100%;
      background:
        repeating-linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          #5c0014,
          #7d001c 20px,
          #3a000d 40px
        );
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 40px #000;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .curtain.left {
      left: 0;
      border-right: 8px solid #2b0009;
    }

    .curtain.right {
      right: 0;
      border-left: 8px solid #2b0009;
    }

    .stage {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      width: min(950px, 100%);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
      line-height: 0.9;
      color: #ffd98a;
      text-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255, 217, 138, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #f3c1d8;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .video-frame {
      background: #14000f;
      border: 12px solid #7a4a16;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 35px rgba(255, 217, 138, 0.25),
        0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      padding: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .video-frame iframe,
    .video-placeholder {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: none;
      background: #000;
    }

    .video-placeholder {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #ffd98a;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #ffd98a;
      color: #180012;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 217, 138, 0.45);
    }

    section {
      padding: 70px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #0c000b;
    }

    section:nth-of-type(even) {
      background: #160013;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #ffd98a;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 18px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #f5ddeb;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .schedule {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: 35px auto 0;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 217, 138, 0.25);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      color: #ffd98a;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      background: #050005;
      color: #caa9ba;
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .curtain {
        width: 16%;
      }

      .stage {
        padding: 10px;
      }

      .video-frame {
        border-width: 7px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="hero">
    <div class="curtain left"></div>
    <div class="curtain right"></div>

    <div class="stage">
      <h1 class="logo">Midnights<br>with Maddie</h1>
      <p class="tagline">New stand-up every Friday at midnight</p>

      <div class="video-frame">
        <!-- 
          Replace the src below with Maddie's weekly YouTube embed link.
          Example:
          https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID
        -->

        <div class="video-placeholder">
          This Week’s Comedy Set Drops Friday at Midnight
        </div>

        <!-- Use this when ready:
        <iframe 
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID"
          title="Midnights with Maddie"
          allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
        -->
      </div>

      <a class="button" href="#episodes">Watch the Latest</a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <section id="episodes">
    <h2>This Week’s Set</h2>
    <p>
      Welcome to the late-night corner of the internet where Maddie takes the stage
      every Friday at midnight with a fresh stand-up comedy video.
    </p>
    <p>
      Bookmark the page, dim the lights, and come back weekly for new jokes,
      new stories, and whatever chaos Maddie brings to the mic.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Upcoming Shows</h2>

    <div class="schedule">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Friday</h3>
        <p>New comedy video premieres at midnight.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Weekly</h3>
        <p>A fresh set, clip, rant, story, or stage moment from Maddie.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Late Night</h3>
        <p>Built for night owls, comedy fans, and people who should be asleep.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>About Maddie</h2>
    <p>
      Maddie is bringing stand-up comedy to the internet one midnight Friday at a time.
      This is her digital stage, complete with curtains, spotlight, and zero drink minimum.
    </p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2026 Midnights with Maddie · New videos every Friday at midnight
  </footer>
</body>
</html>